transcripts: This is the to Breville Juice Fountain Elite. Breville was the first company to introduce the 3 inch tube so you can actually juice whole fruits without having to cut them down to size and it's so powerful that you can juice fruit with the rime on it. So let's get going. So we're just going to turn it on and that powerful motor gets going juicing whole fruit and fruit with the rime on. Another tip is to put a plastic bag in the pulp container because it is so easy to clean like that or you can put your pulp into the compost or even in baking so there is one hundred percent to use. And everything is dishwasher-safe so you just unsnap it and then put all the parts in the dishwasher. Another great Innovation by Breville
